These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: german, egyptian, colombian, malaysian, nigerian, british, indian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rowing, ice-hockey, skateboarding, cricket, swimming, weightlifting, lacrosse
 1. the german is between the malaysian and the indian##2
 2. the egyptian is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the malaysian##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the nigerian is on the left of the british##1
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
11. the british is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | german | indian | egyptian    | colombian | nigerian   | british    |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | ice-hockey   | cricket | rowing | skateboarding   | lacrosse | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: tomato, kale, cucumber, lemon, cherry, radish, plum
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican, american, thai, brazilian, egyptian, dutch
1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating radish and the egyptian##2
3. the mexican is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the american##1
5. the person eating kale is in the middle##1
6. the brazilian is on the left of the nigerian##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person eating kale##1
8. the person eating cherry is on the left of the thai##1
9. the person eating lemon is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | cherry | cucumber | radish | kale | plum | tomato      | lemon  |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai  | dutch     | american     | brazilian  | nigerian | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, italian, russian, indonesian, british, malaysian, chinese
7 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, chinchilla, cat, mouse, lizard, hedgehog
 1. the british is on the left of the japanese##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is the chinese##1
 4. the russian is on the left of the malaysian##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the indonesian is the owner of the cat##1
 7. the japanese is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the hedgehog and the indonesian##2
 9. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the italian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | chinese | british | japanese | italian   | indonesian | russian | malaysian |
| Pet           | mouse | lizard     | ferret     | chinchilla | cat   | dog   | hedgehog    |

