.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, milk, 7up, mirinda, coffee
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, american, british, italian, canadian, indonesian, japanese
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the british##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the canadian##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the italian##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the canadian##1
 5. the russian is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the italian is between the person drinking soy-milk and the indonesian##2
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the italian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the american##1
10. the russian is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | 7up  | milk  | almond-milk  | coffee      | mirinda       | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | canadian | italian | indonesian | japanese | russian | british | american  |

