.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, jazz, soul, r&b, trance, pop, reggae
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, scooter, airplane, jet-ski, bus, quad-bike
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of jazz##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the fan of reggae and the fan of techno##2
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person driving the car is the fan of r&b##1
9. the fan of trance is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | trance | techno | soul | reggae      | jazz      | pop |
| Transport     | car | bus | quad-bike       | snowmobile | scooter | jet-ski | airplane |

