.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  police-officer, entrepreneur, coach, designer, mechanic, social-worker, bartender
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, weightlifting, surfing, soccer, ice-hockey, biathlon, tennis
1. the coach is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the police-officer##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
8. the social-worker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | mechanic | police-officer | designer | social-worker | entrepreneur | coach     | bartender |
| Sport   | surfing   | soccer    | tennis    | ice-hockey      | weightlifting  | baseball | biathlon |

