.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, soy-milk, 7up, water, tea, mirinda
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, handball, snowboarding, tennis, baseball, sailing
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person drinking water##2
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite    | 7up | soy-milk   | tea | mirinda    | water |
| Sport      | snowboarding | ice-hockey | sailing    | skateboarding | tennis    | handball | baseball  |

