.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, sprite, 7up, milk, coffee, iced-tea
The people have 7 different jobs:  scientist, manager, chef, journalist, electrician, pilot, writer
 1. the electrician is on the left of the journalist##1
 2. the scientist is on the left of the chef##1
