 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 7. the manager is on the right of the pilot##1
 8. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
11. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | milk   | soy-milk         | almond-milk     | iced-tea              | coffee    | 7up     |
