The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, ship, car, scooter, van, roller, jet-ski
1. the person watching western movies is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the van##2
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
