.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, almond-milk, sprite, juice, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, baking, skydiving, card-games, drawing, dancing, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is baking##2
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | hot-chocolate       | soy-milk         | juice         | sprite   | almond-milk        | iced-tea |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | skydiving | woodworking | drawing | baking | dancing | card-games  |

