7. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
