 3. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the fan of techno##2
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 7. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching action movies is the fan of metal##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
