 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the fan of hip-hop and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 4. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking water and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
