 6. the person eating cucumber is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is the person eating plum##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 9. the person drinking pearade is between the person drinking 7up and the person eating cucumber##2
10. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
